☐ Wallpaper is not set in greeter, just the background
    - Need to modify user's background file (involves dbus)
    - Importance reduced due to the new Greeter that only shows a small image card.

☐ Use a custom headerbar theme to make the app appear like yin-yang
    - Dark Mode
        - Header Light
        - Background Dark
    - Light Mode
        - Header Dark
        - Background Light
